{"url":"https://www.freightwaves.com/news/navistar-parent-traton-worries-about-impact-of-war-in-ukraine","title":"Navistar parent Traton worries about impact of war in Ukraine","subtitle":"Navistar contribution to truck and bus orders and sales boosts Q1 results","author":"Alan Adler","date":"Wednesday, May 4, 2022","thumbnail":null,"caption":"  Traton reported solid Q1 results despite supply chain disruptions and the war in Ukraine. (Photo: Traton Group)","content":"<div class=\"stream-item stream-item-above-post-content\"><div id=\"div-gpt-ad-1597067535932-0\" data-google-query-id=\"CLaBuIqP1PcCFQUCXAodHiwKHQ\">  <div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/21776187881/FW-Responsive-Main_Content-Slot1_0__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none; margin: auto; text-align: center;\"><iframe id=\"google_ads_iframe_/21776187881/FW-Responsive-Main_Content-Slot1_0\" name=\"google_ads_iframe_/21776187881/FW-Responsive-Main_Content-Slot1_0\" title=\"3rd party ad content\" width=\"468\" height=\"60\" scrolling=\"no\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" role=\"region\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" tabindex=\"0\" srcdoc=\"\" data-google-container-id=\"1\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom;\" data-load-complete=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></div><div data-beyondwords-player=\"true\" contenteditable=\"false\" id=\"beyondwords-player-667d749e-22ac-4fe3-b573-b36ebab24280\" data-beyondwords-init=\"true\">  <div class=\"sk-app-container sk-mod-showing\" style=\"color:#3475b6;--sk-text-color:#111;--sk-link-color:var(--sk-color_silver);--sk-link-color--hover:var(--sk-color_black);background-color:#F5F5F5;\"><button type=\"button\" title=\"play\" name=\"playBtn\" class=\"sk-button-reset sk-play-button svelte-rnhksn\" style=\"\"><svg class=\"sk-icon svelte-isbism\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"32px\" height=\"32px\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\"><g stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"M10.699,6.667 v18.666 L25.365